comments: Millsap (DEN) jumps vertically and absorbs contact when defending Lillard's (POR) driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) slightly extends his arm against Harkless during the pick but the contact is marginal.
Kanter (POR) makes incidental contact with Jokic's (DEN) body after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and McCollum (POR) engage during the pick and switch, and then disengage.
Kanter (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Craig (DEN) and gives him room to avoid contact.
RAR shows Jokic (DEN) puts his forearm/arm to McCollum's (POR) front and arms, and affects his ability to control the ball.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a legal position in Harkless's (POR) path after the dribble hand-off and does not deliver contact.
Harkless (POR) makes marginal contact with Murray (DEN) defending through the pick and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Kanter (POR) makes  contact to Jokic's (DEN) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
LAR shows Millsap (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Kanter (POR) after securing the rebound. Any ensuing contact is considered incidental.
Harkless (POR) briefly grasps Jokic's (DEN) arm but does not affect his ability to get to the ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Turner (POR) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
LLB shows Millsap (DEN) makes marginal contact with Turner (POR) as he tries to dislodge the ball.
Craig (DEN) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) in transition that does not affect his SQBR.
Harris (DEN) makes contact with McCollum (POR) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Harris (DEN) makes incidental contact to the hand of McCollum (POR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Millsap (DEN) and Kanter (POR) engage for the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harkless (POR) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Murray (DEN) slightly extends his arm against Harkless (POR) at the end of his drive but does not affect his ability to defend the play.
McCollum (POR) comes to a stop and releases from Craig (DEN) at the end of his drive with about 13.5 seconds remaining.
Craig (DEN) maintains legal guarding position on Lillard (POR) and makes hand on ball contact as he goes for the steal attempt.
Harkless (POR) makes contact with Murray (DEN) after the screen but does not affect his FOM.
Curry (POR) makes contact to the arm of Jokic (DEN) that affects his ability to gather the ball.  The foul occurs after the pass is thrown in Jokic's direction.
Millsap (DEN) makes contact to Turner's (POR) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Craig (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harkless (POR) and does not give Harkless (POR) a step to avoid contact but he is able to defend through the play.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lillard (POR) and makes marginal contact that does not prevent him to disengage from the play.
Jokic (DEN) pushes off Lillard (POR) to create space for the pass.
Lillard (POR) makes tactile contact to Jokic's (DEN) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) attempts a take foul on Turner (POR) but contact is marginal.
